Interface TokenProxy

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractSignatureWrapper, AbstractTokenProxy, CertificateRevocationWrapper, CertificateWrapper, RelatedCertificateWrapper, RelatedRevocationWrapper, RevocationWrapper, SignatureWrapper, TimestampWrapper
public interface TokenProxy
Interface providing user-friendly API for dealing with JAXB objects from a DiagnosticData
